{"tid":2445794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：香港將繼續從一國兩制中獲得巨大收益","createTime":"2021-03-14T02:20:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T02:25:06.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"de1ceb08bdcd205b2660b6777d02617f0353642e","tid":2445794,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:20:19.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波在一個電台節目指，本港展開疫苗接種計劃，希望控制疫情，恢復商業活動，期望下半年經濟有較強復蘇動力，預測今年經濟增長介乎3.5%至5.5%之間。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，香港將繼續從一國兩制中獲得巨大收益，參與粵港澳大灣區等將是巨大商機。 <br />\n<br />\n陳茂波提到，政府面對財赤，沒有減少在教育、社會福利及健康護理的撥款，財政預算案提出將股票印花稅稅率由0.1%增至0.13%，是要增加政府收入及減少財赤，明白沒有人會喜歡交更多稅，政府已選擇影響最細的範疇加稅，現時並非調整薪俸稅及利得稅的時候。他又說，電子消費券的目的是刺激消費及保持就業。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2382908&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfGaNvfBTe1ydx6p2nKz01sw%3D&h=b897b184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2382908</a>"},{"pid":"c09035732f29a8d71595d4630c30055a2ddfedbf","tid":2445794,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:20:59.000Z","msg":"佢又分裂国家"},{"pid":"92ec2eb64d08372b1c2165106a00cc617184422d","tid":2445794,"uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5LVkpPV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5LVkpPV.jpg&h=ea1d666e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIllusionist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b42f63325ae2f2b61f11703680a0949fc67f158","tid":2445794,"uid":26367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:21:19.000Z","msg":"😂😂笑撚死 今年 -3.5% 就有份"},{"pid":"dea6c2139dc6c1b55e4ab9bea7fb4e34e7fa79cf","tid":2445794,"uid":370972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:22:06.000Z","msg":"大部分香港中產走佬<br />\n等香港變廢港"},{"pid":"ad152c6486456815ae7e0c8fdb9e0a66ad2ced7a","tid":2445794,